cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with image recognition and natural language processing, which are both subfields of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the brain's strategy for associating language stimuli with visual objects, which falls under the category of cognitive science (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper uses deep convolutional neural networks, which are a popular tool in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
